Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在發生各種各樣亂七八糟的事情之後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家終於對戰鬥的目的這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像懂了又好像沒懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又再增加 令人喘不過氣的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦，NERGAL先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『機動戰艦』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍著痛苦所踢起的小石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若反彈回來也會變成鑽芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上到手的夢想不算是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是請堅信它一定會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡從不氣餒的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想哭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠永遠在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的方式驕傲地去面對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去熱衷的日子是夢的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那些碎片收集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能看見 以明天為目標的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOING YOUR DAY'S GROW UP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，你肚子痛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了，走開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你一個 提起精神的訣竅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼晴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，你做什麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又作夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經都是十幾年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡的作戰 『接吻嗎?』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在刷牙洗臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督已經來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟那傢伙合不來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在懷疑 山田少尉的那件事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事不是已經有一位\N提督的部下自首了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也經過軍法審判了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下艦長又會不安心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很突然，不過這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說NERGAL與軍方達成了協定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但命令移交的部份 認可我們有拒絕權
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於違反 本艦所有成員意見的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我御統百合香必須 以艦長的身份加以拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是 不願意做個戰爭的棋子是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們的命令 不是叫你們去打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要你們避開敵人的耳目 完成救出作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出作戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有遭到木星的攻擊 也要保護尊貴的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這撫子的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不得不達成對吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見 目前有2637個鬱金香在地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是北極海的 烏查茲拉瓦特斯克島
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出被留在島上的 某國親善大使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我們的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會留在這種地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大使的好奇心旺盛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果調查北極海的氣象資料 漁場等等的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被蚱蜢襲擊的話就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏查茲拉瓦特斯克島 附近海域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前每天都遭到暴風雪侵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是要經過這裡就很困難了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹馬的感情也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來他和新女朋友 也沒更進一步發展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再談情說愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠完成這作戰的 除了撫子沒別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎? 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我們行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子要前往 烏查茲拉瓦特斯克島了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之沒我們駕駛員的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以養精蓄銳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以好好的養精蓄銳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你缺乏鍛練吶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話可不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是有事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事問我?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…不，百合香的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你馬子吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然問這個幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有心上人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候就決定 托付終身給很棒的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擅自決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你沒那個意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御統百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用打的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實戰是沒啥卑鄙之分的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再比一次接近戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY…GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將進入白令海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於暴風雪，視界為零
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對地，對敵人來說 也是最糟的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未必是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然無法正確判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也沒有會成為障礙的巖礁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以從中央突破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎出力降到最低
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚真像洋娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強尼真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親少女的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝模作樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會這麼說表示劍你很在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦，小孩子給我閉嘴 明人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你離開工作崗位沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島的附近都被暴風雪遮蔽\N無法通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我很閒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人也一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說這次作戰 泉一個人就能應付了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，只要敵人不出現的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之舞台設定成 21世紀初左右的高中可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於服裝等 照標準設定的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來說明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間是為了要紓解乘員\N長期處在宇宙空間的精神壓力而設置的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自動測量各自的腦波\N還有其他資料進行精神分析
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣嚕，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去只屬於我們兩個人的校園生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣，好看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠…你的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時代的裙子好短
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道是第一次 面對這種狀況?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡設定明人是 和我同一個社團的學長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，放輕鬆放輕鬆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼緊張的話 沒辦法紓解壓力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我怎麼不緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，你是怎麼了? 明人學長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來設定得稍微成人化一點 是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，琉璃你擔心嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是和明人去虛擬實驗室了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沈浸於甜蜜的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是約會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得火熱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，御統艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰行動中怎麼可以這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是太過這樣 才會讓他跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉娜小姐只是個操舵士 為什麼那麼囂張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她曾是  NERGAL會長的秘書嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難免驕縱成性…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位快回各自的崗位上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也隨時待命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎? 艦長，態度要嚴厲點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人… 你真的比較喜歡小惠嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，幹嘛把門鎖上?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說有事要商量 到底什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人學長，我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於這次繪畫比賽的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你用我當繪畫的模特兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，什麼? 原來是這樣設定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，突然這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是為了學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不可以，小惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還只是高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方障礙完全清除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始切換為自動駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…艦長…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都去吃午飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃了，琉璃你也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『晚安』\N我喜欢明人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…明人你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長你太軟弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明奪走了我的初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠，總之你先把這個穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長，你討厭我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我最喜歡學長了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是…明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也跟小惠在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『自動迎擊系統開始』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，只要你吻我 我會再加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急狀況 莫非我們被敵人發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續維持力場後退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元歪曲防壁出現安定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到敵人射程外還有十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類似敵方機動部隊重力反應 多數確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃到什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在考慮中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持現狀速度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS隊準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是根據金屬探測 推定的敵方數量和位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必刻意去招呼敵方呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的事就讓它過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生要向前看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要追究責任的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是離開工作崗位的我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程式管理是我的職責 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃難道是在包庇艦長嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不再白癡白癡了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先，如果要避開 已經被敵方發現的西側水道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好從東邊的群島部鑽過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低空飛行時觸礁的可能性 有百分之七十二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是艱難的狀況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子十分鐘之後出發 \N『休息中』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路線是往東側的水路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS隊 採取警戒態勢待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是艦長跑到哪裡去呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能一個人悲慟欲絕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，天河…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我沒資格說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這麼消沈 一點也不像你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長，由於我的疏忽 而連累了所有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣又笨又鈍的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長你也會討厭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我一定會更加努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教你一個恢復精神的訣竅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人 你該不會是在同情我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同情?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在火星的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然說過 只要你吻我，我會再加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你為了我好而沒這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那個時候一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解你當時的的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，你不是我的避風港
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的喜歡我再吻我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為… 這是我最重要的初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行員在緊急待命不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來遲了，非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請報告目前狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦正在巖礁區域行進畔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能在這種地方耽擱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點 可別讓親善大使給餓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前早就 用光燃料凍死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香，給我大使的島的座標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座標參照地圖A-l3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他四機掩護撫子及明人機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 所有便宜都讓你給佔盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對艦長有意思的話 就保護好撫子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊，金鳳花隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大使…大使呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，能源都快用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下真的完蛋啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊… 視線太差，根本打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，用這個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼爆焰…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會回來的，那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河君呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在路上…會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別喪氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓女人流淚啊，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算徹底利用能源 應該也只能再飛十五秒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電波障礙清除 可以使用無線電了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS機體訊號無法確認
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊也沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，親善大使啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會，都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的疏忽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把我回收嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在什麼地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正下方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人機，現在歸艦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過提督 親善大使是指牠嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說要你們賭命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去保護軍方花大筆預算 用實驗器材組合的偵查熊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概沒有人會去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，明人，我好擔心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說，我呀，一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我得去向艦長報告了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了，艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了…不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真的忘記了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的感動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:21:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有純粹的情感沈睡其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要追尋夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容與淚水的數目 就會漸漸增多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時想要更像自我地去感受風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不屬於其他人的我自己的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去發掘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暢銷中的我們的主題歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNING
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順從自我，做你自己，做我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人就是男人，女人就是女人的時代已經遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在索性地問
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:22:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男人昧，有女人昧的活著的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家熟知的  Saber Marionette J原作者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將向問題作挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下回，機動戰艦撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人味是危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起看哦
